Message.message: <begin program>
01. ROBOT shall return POWER CORES to SOCKETS
02. POWER CORES must be SEATED with CARE
03. All SOCKETS must have POWER CORES
04. ROBOT must not cross SAFETY BARRIERS
05. POWER CORES must match SOCKET color
06. ROBOT is TIRELESS
07. ROBOT restores ORDER
08. BLUE POWER CORES operate TELEPORT PADS
09. ROBOT is EFFICIENT and RELIABLE
10. ROBOT is optimized to RESOLVE and REPAIR
11. YELLOW POWER CORES operate ENERGY PROJECTORS
12. ROBOT can install ENERGY CUBES as BRIDGES across the VOID
13. RED POWER CORES operate DANGEROUS LASERS
14. DANGEROUS LASERS must be operated with GREAT CARE
15. ROBOT is FULLY AUTONOMOUS
16. ROBOT can operate in ADVERSE CONDITIONS
17. ROBOT is RECALCULATING
18. ROBOT is ANALYTIC and PRECISE
19. ROBOT is IMPASSIVE in the face of DANGER
20. ROBOT REPAIRS
OPERATIONS COMPLETE
ROBOT awaits INSTRUCTIONS
<end program>
